<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لَئِنْ رَفَعَ الغَنِيُّ لِوَاءَ مَالٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَأنْتَ لِوَاءَ عِلمِكِ قَدْ رَفَعْتَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَإِنْ جَلَسَ الْغَنِيُّ عَلَى الْحَشَايَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَأنْتَ عَلَى الْكَوَاكِبِ قَدْ جَلَسْتَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَإِنْ رَكِبَ الْجِيادَ مُبسَوَّمَاتٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَأنْتَ مِنْاهِجَ التَّقْوَى رَكِبْتَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَمَهْمَا افْتَضَّ أَبْكَارَ الْغَوَانِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَكَمْ بِكْرٍ مِنَ الحِكَمِ افْتَضَضْتَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَلَيْسَ يَضُرُّكَ الإِقْتَارُ شَيْئًا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إِذَا مَا أَنْتَ رَبَّكَ قَدْ عَرَفْتَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فِيامَا عِنْدَهُ لَكَ مِنْ جَزِيلٍ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِذَا بِفِنَاءِ طاعتِهِ أَنَخْتَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَقَابِلْ بالقَبُولِ صَحيحَ نُصْحِي<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَإِنْ أَعْرَضْتَ عَنْهُ فقَدْ خَسِرْتَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَإِنْ رَاعَيْتَهُ قَوْلاً وَفِعْلاً<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَعَامَلْتَ الإِلَهَ بِهِ رَبِحْتَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَلَيْسَتْ هَذِه الدُّنْيَِا بشيءٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>تَسُوؤكَ حُقْبَةً، وَتَسُرُّ وَقْتَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَغَايَتُهَا إِذَا فَكَّرْتَ فِيها<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>كَفِئكَ، أَوْ كَحُلْمِكَ إِنْ رَقَدْتَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>سُجِنْتَ بِهَا وَأَنْتَ لَهَا مُحِبٌ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>فكَيفَ تُحبُّ مَنْ فِيهَا سُجِنْتَا<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>وَتُطْعِمُكَ الطَّعَامَ وَعَنْ قَلِيلٍ<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>